Class ColorChooser

  • java.lang.Object
    • ColorChooser

  • public class ColorChooser
extends java.lang.Object
    Version:
    1.0 This is a program that will allow the user to preview a RGB color code utilizing three separate sliders to change the color composition of Red, Green, and Blue. At the bottom of the sliders will show the color preview of the current value settings on the slider. The sliders will adjust values or they can be manually typed into and it will automatically update to the newest color.
    Author:
    Alex Wong wong4a@gmail.com
